mus, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/150061/', '[1] "Product Information. Zeposia (ozanimod)." Celgene Corporation, Summit, NJ.[2] "Product Information. Zeposia (ozanimod)." Celgene Corporation, Summit, NJ.', 1767369485);
